The Steinberg ASIO SDK is required to build the ASIO driver component.
Due to Steinberg's licensing terms, the ASIO SDK is NOT included in this
repository. Please download it separately from www.steinberg.net and place
it in the docs/ASIOSDK/ directory before building.
